    "Thirdly, this study examines the challenges and potential solutions to the social problems encountered by diffusion models when utilised for image generation.",
    "The aim of this work is to synthesise the extensive body of knowledge scattered across a wide range of publications, distil the key findings and present them in a coherent manner that will facilitate future research efforts.",
    "By providing a comprehensive overview of diffusion models in image generation, this survey aims to serve as a valuable resource for both novice researchers and experienced professionals wishing to deepen their knowledge or explore new avenues of research in this dynamic and evolving field.",
